        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">S+LAUGHTER</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">surprise!</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">B+LOCK</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">BLOCK</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">C+LOCK</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">CLOCK</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">T+RAINING</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">TRAINING</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">W+HALE</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">WHALE</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">P+LACE</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">PLACE</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Setting Up Hook Traps</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Position near TWS:</span> Play a word so its end is one square from a triple-word square. Next turn, hook with S and your new word crosses TWS for 3x scoring.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Use obscure front hooks:</span> Most know CAREŌåÆCARES but few know LAUGHTERŌåÆSLAUGHTER. Study unusual front hooks for plays opponents won't see coming.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Hold S tiles:</span> S is worth 1 point but its hooking power is worth 20+. Never play S unless it adds 8-10+ points over the next-best play without it.</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Surprising Hooks to Memorise</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">HOST ŌåÆ GHOST</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">G front hook. Creates a completely different word. Rarely spotted by opponents.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">RAVE ŌåÆ BRAVE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">B front hook. Works with RAVEN, RAVING too ŌĆö the whole family hooks with B.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">UTTER ŌåÆ BUTTER</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">B front hook. Transforms adjective to noun. Unexpected and rarely challenged.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">ANGER ŌåÆ DANGER</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">D front hook. Part of -ANGER family (HANGER, BANGER, RANGER).</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">­¤ÆĪ Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">The S tile is the <span class="text-white font-medium">most powerful hook letter</span> ŌĆö worth 1 point but capable of adding 20-30+ through premium square access. Never waste S on low-value plays. Hold it for hooks landing on TWS or DWS positions.</p>
      </div>
